ygData.subject: Re: Qyenos Merchant that sells tiny daggers?
ygData.msgSnippet: You might do a /who all enchanters to see all the enchanters in the world and look for those in Erudin.  You could then /tell someone and ask if they would
ygData.messageBody:
You might do a /who all enchanters to see all the enchanters in the
world and look for those in Erudin. You could then /tell someone and
ask if they would pick you up some if coming to Qeynos.

-----Original Message-----
From: mark Prescott [mailto:prescotm@...]
Sent: Thursday, April 29, 1999 3:53 PM
To: eqenchanters@onelist.com
Subject: [eqenchanters] Re: Qyenos Merchant that sells tiny daggers?


From: "mark Prescott" <prescotm@...>

I dont think you can buy the daggers in Qeynos..but a shot boat ride to
Erudin and you buy a bunch from the echanter guild there
----- Original Message -----
From: <clark@...>
To: <eqenchanters@onelist.com>
Sent: Thursday, April 29, 1999 10:33 AM
Subject: [eqenchanters] Qyenos Merchant that sells tiny daggers?


> From: clark@...
>
> I have traveled for many days and nights, and fought off countless
perils
to reach the Human city of Qyenos. It it very different than my home
city of
Ak'anon but I find myself drawn to explore and learn. Since I have
decided
to stay in Qyenos for a while I will need an animation to protect myself
from the smelly gnolls. Can any fellow enchanters tell me the location
of
the merchant in Qyenos that will sell me tiny daggers?
>
> Thanks Kindly
>
> Agergon (Tunare)
